2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper proposes a relay selection strategy for a wireless network, which is a key aspect of networking and internet architecture. The paper also discusses the use of space-time codes and beamforming techniques for retransmitting data, which are important topics in networking.
3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper deals with the design and analysis of a relay system with HARQ, which can be viewed as a control system. The paper also proposes a relay selection strategy, which can be seen as a control problem.
4. cs.COMM (Computer Communications and Networks) - The paper deals with the design and analysis of a wireless relay network, which is a key aspect of computer communications and networks.
